Package: swotr
Type: Package
Title: Functions for SWOT-like Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Mark", "Hagemann", email = "mark.hagemann@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Contains utility functions including data input, cleaning,
    processing, and plotting, for river datasets of the kind to be gathered
    in the upcoming Surface Water and Ocean Topography (SWOT) NASA/CNES 
    mission.
